quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  17,59,"Ntakituzitira kuzana ibitangaro mugabo nuko abantu bakera babihakanye, duca tubaha abantu bo kwa Thamudu Ingamiya y’inyana kuba arico kimenyetso kiri k’umugaragaro mugabo baramuhakanye, natwe ntidutwara ivyo bimenyetso atari ukubagabisha"
  17,60,"Mugihe twakubwira duti:- mu vy’ukuri Umuremyi wawe aramaze kubakikuza abo bantu babi, kandi natwe ntitwagize yandoto twakwereka atari ukuba gerageza abantu n’igiti cavumwe canditswe mugitabu c’Imana gitagatifu ca Qur’ani nukuba gabisha, mugabo ntaco vyabongereje atari ukwiyonkora kuniniya"
  17,61,"Mugihe twabwira Abamarayika duti:- nimu pfukamire intumwa y’Imana Adamu (iii), bose baramu pfukamiye dukuyemwo uwitwa Ibilisi yavuze ati:- mbega jewe nopfukamira umwe waremwe mw’ivu"
  17,62,"Avuga ati :- urabona uyu wahaye iteka gusumba jewe, rero umpaye umwanya kugeza k’umusi w’imperuka, ntankeka jewe nzohonya uruvyaro rwiwe rwose dukuyemwo bakeyi gusa"
  17,63,"Imana ivuga iti:- mvira ngaho uwuzo gukurikira muribo mu vy’ukuri umuriro udahera witiriwe Jahannamu niwo uzoba ari impembo yanyu ikwiye"
  17,64,"Niwegeranye abo ushoboye bose muribo kw’ijwi ryawe kandi wegeranye aburira ifarasi n’abagenda n’amaguru, kandi ushigikirane nabo mumatungo yabo hamwe n’ibibondo vyabo, kandi ubemerere mugabo Shetani ntiha abagira indagano atari z’ububeshi gusa"
  17,65,"Mu vy’ukuri abashumvyi banje ntabutegetsi ubafitiyeko, n’Umuremyi wawe arahagije kuba ariwe abakingira"
  17,66,"Umuremyi wanyu nurya aba gendeshereza amato yanyu mubiyaga kugira ngo murondere imigisha yayo, ntankeka niyo nyene impuhwe kuri mwebwe bantu"